    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="text-gray-600 mb-8">
          This page contains information about how we collect, use and protect your personal information.
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Information We Collect</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          [Privacy policy content to be completed according to specific needs]
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">
          [Information about personal data usage]
        </p>
        
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mt-8 mb-4">Contact</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          For questions about this privacy policy, you can contact us at: 
          <a href="mailto:janna.ziesemer@googlemail.com" class="text-blue-600 hover:text-blue-700">
            janna.ziesemer@googlemail.com
